original_title: Muse: Live at Stubb's Bar-B-Q (South By Southwest) 2010
overview: Announced two days before the show, Muse played a set at Stubb's Bar-B-Q during the annual South By Southwest (SXSW) Music Festival. Though the entire set was to be streamed live on MySpace the following night, due to sound recording issues only two songs (Stockholm Syndrome and Knights of Cydonia) were made available.  Austin, Texas  19th March 2010
title: Muse: Live at Stubb's Bar-B-Q (South By Southwest) 2010
